T1  - Aggregation and identification in consumer demand systems
AU  - Heineke, J.M.
AU  - Shefrin, H.M.
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 44
IS  - 3
SP  - 377
EP  - 390
PY  - 1990
